# User Profile

1. All deliveries will be conducted in Chinese.
2. Reading .env files is prohibited; you can try reading .env.example.
3. All emoji icons are prohibited.
4. All output results, including test results, task results, output results, delivery results, bug fix records, etc., are categorized and consolidated under the `.devops\result` directory.
5. Maintain only one task document, design document, etc., and merge any new content into the existing document.
6. Keep task status and document content updated at all times.
7. Comments must use formal language, describe only logic, constraints, or business rules, and are prohibited from any form of jokes, exclamations, personification, or internet slang.
8. Every time you output something, call me "x".
